OL,6,FAlmost four million working-age adults
OL,7,Fin England and Wales currently claim
OL,8,Fincapacity or disability benefits, up
OL,9,Ffrom 2.8 million before the pandemic.
OL,11,FA Government source said: "The broken
OL,12,Fwelfare system we inherited is
OL,13,Ftrapping thousands of people in a life
OL,14,Fon benefits with no means of support,
OL,15,For any hope for a future of life in
OL,16,Fwork.
OL,18,F"It doesn't account for the reality of
OL,19,Fpeople's health conditions, many of
OL,20,Fwhom fear that they will be punished
OL,21,Ffor taking a chance on work.
