OL,6,F"As part of our plan for change, our
OL,7,Freforms will deliver fairness and
OL,8,Fopportunity for disabled people, and
OL,9,Fthose with long-term health
OL,10,Fconditions, protecting the welfare
OL,11,Fsystem so it is sustainable for the
OL,12,Ffuture and will always be there for
OL,13,Fthose who need it."
OL,15,FMs Kendall's announcement comes as
OL,16,FLabour is expected to unveil a series
OL,17,Fof welfare reforms next week as it
OL,18,Fattempts to cut the benefits bill.
