OL,6,FJames Taylor, executive director at
OL,7,Fdisability charity Scope, said giving
OL,8,Fdisabled people "greater confidence to
OL,9,Ftry work" was "a good move", but
OL,10,Fwarned against making significant cuts
OL,11,Fto benefits.
OL,13,FHe said: "We hope that releasing news
OL,14,Fof this scheme at this time isn't a
OL,15,Fsmokescreen designed to blur the lines
OL,16,Fbetween in and out of work benefits.
OL,18,F"(Personal independence payment)
OL,19,Fexists because life costs more if you
OL,20,Fare disabled. It isn't an out of work
OL,21,Fbenefit.
