OL,6,F"Making it harder to get benefits will
OL,7,Fjust push even more disabled people
OL,8,Finto poverty, not into jobs."
OL,10,FAsked about Labour's welfare plans
OL,11,Fduring a press conference on Saturday,
OL,12,FSir Keir said: "I have made the
OL,13,Fprinciples clear enough. We need to
OL,14,Fsupport those who need support, and to
OL,15,Fprotect them.
OL,17,F"But at the same time we need to make
OL,18,Fsure that we support and protect those
OL,19,Fwho need to and are able to get into
OL,20,Fwork, which the current arrangements I
OL,21,Fdon't think adequately do.
